title: Ep 03- The One Vaccine Newborns Must Avoid [My Incredible Opinion]
description:
Well-meaning nurses will attempt to inject your baby with a vaccination before they are a few hours old. Are there any vaccinations you can safely skip? I’m Forrest Maready and this is my incredible opinion.

Do aluminum vaccine adjuvants contribute to the rising prevalence of autism?
http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/22099159

Hepatitis B immunization induces higher antibody and memory Th2 responses in new-borns than adults.
http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/14670334
